bo_img','field_663a4396ffca7'),(929,87,'abo_title','Once upon a time…'),(930,87,'_abo_title','field_663a43b1ffca8'),(931,87,'abo_content','Maxime Richard is one of the most successful kayakers of all time. A national, European and world champion. He has spent many years chasing performance and the best times. Now a coach and instructor, Maxime also wanted to refocus on his kayaking. For him, it\'s a fantastic way of getting around on the water and setting off on an adventure. After discovering packraft in Slovenia in 2015, he already knew he wasn\'t going to stop there...\r\n\r\nIt will have taken a few years to put his personal approach into practice and come up with a boat that meets all his development requirements. Maxime Richard was able to surround himself with a motivated team of complementary profiles: designers, entrepreneurs, industrial engineers... Left & Right is both an achievement and, above all, the start of a new adventure. Join the movement and find out how Left & Right reinvented packraft!'),(932,87,'_abo_content','field_663a43c1ffca9'),(933,87,'gal_title','Gallery'),(934,87,'_gal_title','field_663a43e1ffcab'),(935,87,'gal_galerie',''),(936,87,'_gal_galerie','field_663a43edffcac'),(937,87,'con_title','Contact'),(938,87,'_con_title','field_663a4428ffcaf'),(939,87,'con_intro','Do you have any questions? Would you like to contact us?\r\n\r\nPlease use the form below or contact Left & Right directly.'),(940,87,'_con_intro','field_663a4437ffcb0'),(941,87,'con_form','[contact-form-7 id=\"9f09927\" title=\"Contact Form EN\"]'),(942,87,'_con_form','field_663a444bffcb1'),(943,87,'pac_title','Packraft Noguera'),(944,87,'_pac_title','field_663a460124434'),(945,87,'pac_intro','Left & Right is another way of paddling. \r\n\r\nIt’s discovering and tackling the water without any compromise. In complete freedom.'),(946,87,'_pac_intro','field_663a461124435'),(948,87,'_pac_img','field_663a463224436'),(949,87,'pac_kpi_0_l1','Streamlined'),(950,87,'_pac_kpi_0_l1','fie